'''DESG (Defence Engineering and Science Group)''' is a community of 9,000 engineers and scientists working within the United Kingdom [[Ministry of Defence (United Kingdom)|Ministry of Defence]] Civil Service to equip and support the UK Armed Forces with military hardware.
==Locations== *[[Bristol]] *[[Andover, Hampshire|Andover]] *[[Wyton]] *[[London]]
==Recruiting== There are 3 main methods of recruiting for DESG, # The Graduate Scheme <ref>http://www.desg.mod.uk/graduateops/graduatescheme.shtml</ref> # Sponsorship while at University in either The DESG University Sponsorship scheme<ref>http://www.desg.mod.uk/studentops/desgsponsorship.shtml</ref>, or the [[Defence Technical Undergraduate Scheme]]([[DTUS]])<ref>http://www.desg.mod.uk/studentops/dtugscheme.shtml</ref> # [[Welbeck Defence Sixth Form College]]<ref>http://www.desg.mod.uk/studentops/welbeck.shtml</ref>
